hudson.tasks.BatchFile.command:
call cd ../../..
call cd desktop
call cd diasp
git clone https://github.com/TIBHannover/diaspora.git
call cd diaspora/wp2/t2.1/v1.0/pipeline/workspace
call xcopy diaspora_to_csv %jenkins_path%\diaspora_to_csv /I /H /C /E
call xcopy diaspora_rdf_map %jenkins_path%\diaspora_rdf_map /I /H /C /E
call xcopy Diaspora_store_to_graph %jenkins_path%\Diaspora_store_to_graph /I /H /C /E
call xcopy Query_diaspora %jenkins_path%\Query_diaspora /I /H /C /E
call xcopy validate_diaspora %jenkins_path%\validate_diaspora /I /H /C /E
call cd %local_repo_path%
call rmdir diaspora /S /Q
